abstract: Brian Davis wins Valspar Championship with six-under-par 65; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Brian Davis of England holds a one-shot lead in the Valspar Championship after a birdie on his final hole.

headline.main: Englishman Leads in the Valspar Championship
